EXTRACTED VALUE: "Evanovich writes with flair in an absurdist vein that her imitators can only envy."
"Steel's fans will be delighted by this story of a woman seduced by a man who is too good to be true."
"A heroine with spunk and spirit offers an inspiring lesson in perseverance and hope."
"Though Nate may not achieve the fame he seeks with his classmates, this sharp-witted and unflappable protagonist just might find it with readers."
"When it comes to telling funny stories about boys, no one surpasses Paulsen, and here he is in top form."
"[I]n [this] compelling sequel....Bagshawe expertly channels Sheldon's lurid, feverish prose." (starred review)
"For my money, nobody talks quality better than Phil Crosby." -Lee Iacocca
